title: 'Dudesons' Star Jukka Hilden Bit By Alligator in INSANE Stunt
text:
EXCLUSIVE 
" The   Dudesons "   star Jukka Hilden -- a member of the four-man stunt group from Finland --   played a game called Alligator Bite Roulette, and it's EXACTLY the way it sounds.
Here's the thing ... after the loser got bit, everyone else wanted a bite taken out of them ... and the gator obliged.
It's bloody ... and crazy.
